cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.SD 

This paper deals with using social media text to estimate suicide risk and mental health, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Additionally, the paper deals with mental health, which could place it in cs.CY (Computers and Society) or cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing).
